&lt;p&gt;OH! No, I didn&apos;t!  Yes, this would be MUCH better to do under markdown.  I&apos;m tempted to move some other docs to that as well. apt is... interesting. &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/wink.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;  Awesome! Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
